title: Will Donald Trump Actually Run For President In 2012?
description: Roland Martin appears on JKUSA to discuss which Republicans will run for president in 2012. Donald Trump continues to keep his name is the mix a as potential candidate for the 2012 presidential race. Michele Bachmann and Mike Pence are keeping their names in the mix as well.
